"Alternatively, you can open a shell by pressing Ctrl+Alt+F2. Use Alt+F5 to "
"get back to the installer."
msgstr ""
"Neu, gallwch agor cragen drwy wasgu Ctrl+Alt+F2. Defnyddiwch Alt+F5 i "
"ddychwelyd i'r sefydlydd."
